          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " The exotic beam was produced using the proton beam",
                "from the cyclotron Cyclone-30 impinging on a LiF powder",
                "target via the reaction Li-7(p,2p)He-6. The atomic beam",
                "was ionized in an ECR ion source, purified by magnetic",
                "separation and post accelerated by a second cyclotron",
                "Cyclone-110 of the CRC facility."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A self-supported foils of Pb-208 with a thickness",
                "of 0.950-mg/cm**2 were used as target.",
                "In order to increase the counting rate at the highest",
                "laboratory energy of 22 MeV a target foil of",
                " 2.080-mg/cm**2 was used.",
                "The targets had the following isotopic composition-",
                "Pb-208 87(2)%, Pb-207 1.20(2)%, Pb-206 11.4(2)%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "82-PB-208(A,EL)82-PB-208,,DA",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "82-PB-208(A,EL)82-PB-208,,DA",
